### Market Contextualization for Ahmedabad Luxury (₹10 Cr+ Segment)
In Ahmedabad, the ₹10 Cr+ segment is shifting from traditional bungalow living in areas like Satellite or Bodakdev to high-rise vertical luxury near the Narmada Canal or the Sabarmati riverfront/lake-facing zones (e.g., Sindhu Bhavan Road extension or Prahlad Nagar). Unlike Mumbai or Delhi, the Ahmedabad HNI is deeply rooted in local industrial legacy (Chemicals, Textiles, Pharmaceuticals, or Solar Energy). They value "Vastu compliance" and "community prestige" above mere architectural vanity. 

