### Data Note
*Research Gap:* While public transaction data for ₹10 Cr+ properties in Ahmedabad is tracked via IGR (Inspector General of Registration), the specific *psychographic* drivers for "lake-view" buyers in Ahmedabad are currently undergoing a shift. Historically, Ahmedabad buyers preferred ground-floor bungalows; the "Vertical Luxury" trend is relatively new. Therefore, the "Pain Point" regarding long-term maintenance is based on historical feedback from high-rise owners in the city who faced operational decay in premium projects after 5-7 years.